Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這怎麼像是手寫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家去觀光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話是這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可就算你說要單獨留守
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不可能真把鈴野你一個人丟下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是沒這麼做過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那地圖只在你那有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,資料好像沒法傳輸出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過以前都從來沒想過觀光這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來也是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近感覺有點不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路線已經轉告你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不用管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等涅伊特醒了一個人都沒有也挺麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H160E10&\3c&HFFFFFF&}我們在道後溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給AI留便條可還行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找人讀給他聽不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去周遊四國啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過把「開關」留下多少有點放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到擬態族也沒法著裝成裝甲少女了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四國迄今從未有過擬態族登陸的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得即便把「開關」送到福岡也不能就撒手不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果決戰在那裡打響的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼下可能就是我們最後的假期了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也沒有送達期限
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又覺得餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就趁機好好遊覽一下四國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多標籤都什麼時候貼上去的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這也太和平了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種四國被排除在了擬態族侵略目標外的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然防衛隊有提醒他們進行警戒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人認為是這裡不出產核心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也有擬態族討厭烏冬的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就該把木盆烏冬推廣到全國才行囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許比「開關」還好用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運輸烏冬可方便得很
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正四國也沒怪獸過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那「開關」到底是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛　只知道是對擬態族的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼個王牌法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京決戰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在防衛隊的通話裡聽他們提到過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是相當厲害的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位女士倒是解釋了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根本聽不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反覆看過錄影
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜測或許是能將擬態族封閉在時空裂隙裡的系統吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或許就有勝算囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來　我要拍囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家把木盆端起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那樣端會灑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果你自己灑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要真能把擬態族全搞定的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我們要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從來都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.24,0:10:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定擬態族之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就一邊找回去原來世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊繼續旅行不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但照這套路搞不好咱們要一起找一輩子哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也未必不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.46,0:10:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過回去的話大家就都要分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易能和大家友好相處了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿她沒轍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們就走橋好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也坐那個過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備--走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直像猴子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒你像喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搖得好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往中間靠一點比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像中更累人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起重我更怕高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野你的路西法不是一直都飄在空中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是兩碼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊　那麼要調頭回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話也稍微有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要休息一會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野　對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回頭還是前進儘快做下決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是這個…要坐這個的事也想和你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想和你說說話才坐這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在京都時候也問過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再確定一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然有什麼事得罪你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告訴我到底哪兒得罪你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常想和鈴野友好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有做什麼得罪我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.15,0:12:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道鈴野你經常會避開我的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會只是單純討厭我這種性格的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不說清楚的話我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊　鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一定要友好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得有緣一起旅行　並肩戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們五個人原本素昧平生　連同學都不算
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過因為同是裝甲少女才在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家通過發揮各自LBX的特性互相扶持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒擬態族並生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是和那麼恐怖的敵人戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道何時會遭遇什麼意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得這樣一起成了朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這方面　很煩人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒想過和大家成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你們一起戰鬥也只是為了生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到自己的世界罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏花不是也說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可不是什麼好朋友集會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一個戰術分隊罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要保持那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是理子來了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊內的氣氛就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.13,0:14:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在可不是該在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.11,0:14:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得這麼開心的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你可能沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是和美春同歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你要大一歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼稱呼我的時候叫得那麼親切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比我小一歲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.68,0:15:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　沒事吧　理子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野就是這種性格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家家有本難唸的經
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起　鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,強行要帶你一起出來我也有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得出來玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要繼續和我們一起玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得她是害怕和我們關係太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是在原來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是到了這邊後遇到過什麼事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就隱約覺得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有過悲傷的離別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是絕對沒有討厭你和我們才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多體諒她一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃不吃鹽味炒粉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用　我肚子不是很餓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我完全沒有考慮過鈴野同學的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得我有點強行把自己的感情加在了你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是像現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作主張買了兩份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會自己吃完的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想你會不會想一個人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常轉校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為家裡的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我經常轉校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此每次都不得不和要好的朋友分別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這樣才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕被你們笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.94,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看　你這不是笑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起　因為太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算把話說開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得會那樣想的鈴野非常厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對　鈴野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以為你是和我同歲或者要小一歲的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了　剛才的聲音可厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為用了Attack Function導致生命值變0了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理子你不也是每晚睡覺肚子都會咕咕叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒也不是每晚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我肚子會在睡著後咕嚕叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去和由衣玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用叫我叫得那麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明比你小一歲哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手啊　由衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓她們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給AI留便條
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也真是夠胡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那突然關機是升級了什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各種各樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五個人和好如初
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烏冬地圖派上用場了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且鈴野小姐一直默默照顧著大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在的話這個隊伍可要玩完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此大家這次能更加融洽相處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的汗馬功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般會說出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說話這傢伙是不是性格大變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的錯覺吧
